Package org.gephi.io.importer.api

Interface EdgeDraft

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ElementDraft
    public interface EdgeDraft
extends ElementDraft
    Draft edge, hosted by import containers to represent edges found when importing. Processors decide if this edge will finally be appended to the graph or not.
    Author:
    Mathieu Bastian
    See Also:
    ContainerLoader

      • isSelfLoop

        boolean isSelfLoop()
        Returns true if this edge is a self-loop.

        It returns false if the source or target is null.

        Returns:
